## ğŸ§° Hardware List

- M5Stack Atom Lite
- IMU Pro Unit (connected to Port A)
- RGB LED Strip (WS2812 or compatible)
- USB-C Cable for power + serial data
- Headband structure or mount (custom or elastic)
